data.description: Come live in Paradise! This gorgeous home is located in the desirable community of Vista Palms right in the heart of Wimauma. This adorable home offers a great floor plan. As you enter the home you are greeted by a large living area with tons of natural lighting and beautiful views of the backyard oasis. The kitchen is perfect for entertaining your guests as it opens up to the living room and dining room. The kitchen offers lots of cabinets, an extended countertop, and a large pantry. The spacious living room offers sliding glass doors with breathtaking views of two ponds and a conservation lot. This home is full of endless possibilities. The split floor plan offers privacy for everyone with 3 bedrooms and a bathroom on one side of the home. The Master bedroom is located right off the living room. Enjoy the views from your Master bedroom overlooking the pond and conservation. The master suite offers plenty of room with a large closet. The Master bathroom has a walk-in shower and dual vanity sinks. Life is too short to fold fitted sheets, but no problem in this large laundry room with plenty of space for all your laundry needs. This home offers outdoor living at its best. The sun is glowing, and the breeze is blowing. It's easy to get lost in this backyard oasis. No need to spend time with lawn care as HOA includes yard maintenance for you. Relax in your backyard where there will be a lot of sipping, grilling, and chilling overlooking amazing views.   Vista Palms is a family-friendly community with amazing amenities consisting of a playground, resort-style pool, fitness center, splash pad, and clubhouse. This home is conveniently located near shopping, Downtown Tampa, Busch Gardens, lots of restaurants, Macdill Air Force Base, and beaches, I-75
